[2026-05-31 18:09:27] local.INFO: Diagnosis Step Output {"diagnosis":{"confidence":0.8,"estimated_price_max":7000,"estimated_price_min":1500,"issue_type":"pipe_leak","recommended_service":"Professional inspection and repair of overhead water tank system","summary":"Water leaking under your overhead water tank could indicate an issue with the tank's connections, overflow pipe, outlet pipe, or the tank body itself. It's important to address this promptly to prevent water wastage, potential damage to your property, and ensure the integrity of your water supply. The estimated cost depends on the source and severity of the leak, and whether parts replacement is needed. We recommend a professional plumber inspect the tank and associated piping to accurately diagnose and repair the leak.","urgency":"medium","provider":"gemini","model":"gemini-2.5-flash"}} 
